Package ru.introguzzle.parsers.json.entityUnion

Interface JSONStringConvertable

All Known Implementing Classes:
JSONArray, JSONObject
public interface JSONStringConvertable
Interface representing an entityUnion that can be converted to a JSON string.

This interface defines methods to retrieve the opening and closing symbols, iterate over its contents, and obtain the size of the entityUnion. It provides default methods for converting the entityUnion to a JSON string in both compact and pretty-printed formats.
